PR ada/114065, patches v15

In the hope to reduce the rebasing work,
when a whole file can be kept unchanged in Debian,
 * files specific to other systems can remain broken
 * cal.c can remain, it is disabled in Makefile.rtl
 * declarations of obsolete but unused time types or constants
the changes affecting it are removed from this patch.

